<title type="html"><![CDATA[10/12Sat.)10 Tips for Saving Money/What’s the Panic Over ‘Joker’ Really About?(Host:Danny)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=324&amp;p=340#p340"><![CDATA[
10/12(Sat.)10 Tips for Saving Money/What’s the Panic Over ‘Joker’ Really About?(Host:Danny)<br /><br />Article 1: 10 Tips for Saving Money<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.vacu.org/learn/financial-management/saving-and-investing/10-tips-for-saving-money">https://www.vacu.org/learn/financial-ma ... ving-money</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion<br />1. Do you have your own way for saving money? How and Why?<br />2. Do you agree to all  the article’s ideas? Why?<br />3. Which one is your favorite way in the article? And you will try it.<br /><br />Article 2: What’s the Panic Over ‘Joker’ Really About?<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.nytimes.com/2019/10/02/magazine/the-joker-movie.html?fallback=0&amp;recId=1Rvg1jQdaIZL62ljHiQ9IIZwuzF&amp;locked=0&amp;geoContinent=AS&amp;geoRegion=NWT&amp;recAlloc=story&amp;geoCountry=TW&amp;blockId=home-featured&amp;imp_id=662396706&amp;action=click&amp;module=editorsPicks&amp;pgtype=Article&amp;region=Footer">https://www.nytimes.com/2019/10/02/maga ... ion=Footer</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1. Have you seen any film about &quot;Joker&quot;, and What is your favorite version about joker? Please share to us. If you haven't seen, please answer next question.<br />2. The clown reflects the social problem. His frustration turn into violence and become the criminal clown. What do you think the crime? Is his problem or a society issue ?<br />3. The protesters are angry with the government because of him. Can you say that they are blind followers? Even if this is not what the joker meant.<br />4. Do you fear of clowns in real life? Why? Why not?<br /><br />Agenda<br />7:00 ~ 7:30 pm greetings &amp; free talk<br />7:30 ~ 8:15 pm guests introduced &amp; first session discussion<br />8:15 ~ 8:45 pm presentation, sharing the article &amp; other experiences<br />8:45 ~ 9:30 pm second session discussion<br /><br />Position: Dante coffee Shop (丹堤咖啡), MRT板南線 - 新埔站2號出口, next to 7-Seven,<br />板橋民生路二段237 號,<br />Time: PM 7:00-9:30,<br />a minimum charge of Dante coffee for Royal English club attendant NT$80 (丹提低消80元)<br />最自由的全英文會話聚會,前三次不用交會費,加入會員終生會費NT$500.請帶著開放與熱情來學英文<br /><br />Royal 三峽 , Royal new branch information,<br />Every Monday evening: 8:00pm- 10pm: 摩斯漢堡 北大特區 土城區學成路712號, next to the park.<br />Please keep contact with President Ophelia.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Thu Oct 10, 2019 1:47 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
